title.rendered: BOSS AIR PX07 COMPLETE 12 VOLT AIR COMPRESSOR

content.rendered:
BOSS AIR PX07 COMPLETE 12 VOLT AIR COMPRESSOR

Boss Air PX07 Complete 12 Volt Air Compressor available for order now through Automax 4×4! Order online, come in & see us or give us a call on (02) 6699 2744 for a quote!

Includes:

  • PX-07 Compressor
  • 110-150psi Pressure Switch
  • 100% Duty Solenoid
  • Check Valve
  • 3/8″ Flare Fitting
  • Teflon Coated Braided Hose

Specs;

  • 12v Air Compressor
  • 3/4 hp engine
  • 100% duty cycle
  • Recommended working pressure 0-150psi maximum pressure 200psi – 31.5 amp maximum draw
  • Fan cooled engine and cylinder head
  • Oil free design
  • 3/8npt ported head
  • Rebuildable design
  • Crank case fed – external washable air filter
  • Cast aluminum legs
  • Special piston valve design for maximum performance

PLEASE NOTE: MUST USE CHECK VALVE TO PREVENT BACK FLOW+ 40 AMP FUSE – NEVER OIL THIS COMPRESSOR

To view the range of Boss Air products available, CLICK HERE!
Follow us on Instagram and Facebook to keep up to date with what’s going on in our workshop!
